# Meet the R-HTA in LMICs Committee ü§ù

> *"The R-HTA in LMICs team comprises individuals from a range of Lower-Middle Income Countries (LMICs). We have a diverse set of skills and backgrounds and hope to share our experiences in learning R for HTA with you!"*

We are a growing team of researchers, economists, data scientists, and public health professionals who are passionate about improving healthcare decision-making in LMICs through open-source tools and collaborative learning.

---

